lead_paragraph: Barcelona coach Luis Enrique was impressed with the way his team performed in their Champions League win at Arsenal on Tuesday, which extended their club record unbeaten run to 33 games.

headline.print_headline: Luis Enrique Delighted as Barca Extend Record Unbeaten Run
